{"tid":1749233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［慈雲西］民建聯選舉日派人上樓做「家訪」","createTime":"2019-11-24T02:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T04:34:17.000Z","uid":1727,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad310ea1966cd99b533fd1e199ee659ec0e294dd","tid":1749233,"uid":1727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"今日行過慈雲西選區民建聯辦事處門口，<br />\n見到一班叔叔嬸嬸企喺門口，<br />\n我就上前八卦下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3o3tNZS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3o3tNZS.jpg&h=3a601787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就見到有一個啊姨，喺到派緊d資料俾其他「義工」，<br />\n而資料係該選區嘅人住咩室，手提電話幾多號。<br />\n而義工都會收到一張流程圖，<br />\n教d義工上到樓要點做，<br />\n但佢遮得太快我影唔到睇唔清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adRrzF9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadRrzF9.jpg&h=2a496264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當有一個年紀較後生嘅女性發現我企喺到聽佢地講解嘅時候，即刻企喺我前面擋住我，唔俾我再接觸班義工同影相。<br />\n<br />\n問我喺到做乜，重申自己今次義工「家訪」係向房屋處申請咗，<br />\n咁我都見到係有申請書。<br />\n<br />\n聽問年年投票都係有呢d「家訪」，<br />\n相信大家都知「家訪」目的。<br />\n我岀post目的係「希望大家關心吓家中嘅長輩」，<br />\n同埋研究下到底咁樣嘅義工「家訪」當中有冇討論空間呢？"},{"pid":"c8586e7d2781d09b750fde39182281d5b1ebbb98","tid":1749233,"uid":1727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9389f85d162f0f1809ca5b44c85538510a29e901","tid":1749233,"uid":1727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"有冇慈雲西居民留意下"},{"pid":"512822d6afbdc2d79d63693b36db4619163592a5","tid":1749233,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:49:38.000Z","msg":"影佢老母先"},{"pid":"ae6ac4a86ed85c8d8998bbbacab0037a45d4d2b3","tid":1749233,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"票站職員話唔得架喎"},{"pid":"1a35c68fe806fdabdadd8e16a9a7fa8524e57a47","tid":1749233,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:17:43.000Z","msg":"用imgur upload"},{"pid":"7a00adf639aafd8311c48db54c6b4f1e3bf8602f","tid":1749233,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:19:38.000Z","msg":"send比英議員啦"},{"pid":"49c093f60e415b641e33627c71816bfca473d1b5","tid":1749233,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"【突發】英國上議院議員來香港監督選舉，有異樣請FB舉報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746728</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e3fc0309ab8557c1e6a2ba2813de15bce49d112","tid":1749233,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"RTHK鏗鏘集：如有任何選舉異常情況 請向91829284報料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1749430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1749430</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"970fddd2c9a86ee792883bfafa32ea2e1c51603f","tid":1749233,"uid":105352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:22:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1fc4eacfe4abe9134fd8f0724f3e26c6731011b","tid":1749233,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"有乜疑似干預選舉情況<br />\n拍片/相&mdash;》<br />\n<br />\n「選舉觀察計劃」報料熱線 Election Observation Hotline<br />\nTelegram: @hotline19hkeop<br />\nWhatsApp: +85297424472<br />\n又或者報料俾傳媒記者（蘋果丶有線丶立場）<br />\n監察7️⃣<br />\n幫傳真社寫做記錄"},{"pid":"425eedd3639d06ec5c396ada70aa88874a1fb827","tid":1749233,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e61d7315f065e59e1f3e42c908681fe789a506","tid":1749233,"uid":1727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e3fc0309ab8557c1e6a2ba2813de15bce49d112","tid":1749233,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"RTHK鏗鏘集：如有任何選舉異常情況 請向91829284報料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1749430\" data-auto-link targe